1. EDA (Exploratory Data Analysis):

Data loading and basic visualizations.
Key statistics and distribution analysis.

2. Lookalike Model:

Merging customer and transaction data.
Computing customer similarity and outputting the top 3 recommendations for the first 20 customers.

3. Clustering:

Feature engineering, normalization, and clustering using KMeans.
Evaluation using the Davies-Bouldin Index and visualizing clusters with PCA.

You can adjust paths to the CSV files and execute each section to complete the tasks.
